task.summary: Configured dexOptions to support more libraries
Replaced image file queue with image database
Cached image now displays in list immediately
Cached receipt image is always shown correctly
Receipts upload automatically on network stage change
Improved camera stability on certain devices
Forced portrait mode across the app
List now only displays unattached receipts
Fixed bug where enviroment preference is visible for all users
Added translations for Norwegian, Norwegian Bokmål
Saves only reference to file in database (Build 36)
Removed business logic from receipt view (Build 38)
Fixed waiting for Internet status message
Finalize and create expense report (build 44, v 1.0)
Various improvement to expense report flow (build 45, v 1.01)
Finalized expense reports cannot be edited/updated (build 46, v 1.0.2)
Delete expense reports and receipts (build 47, v 1.0.3)
Receipt images no longer pop in/out + bug fixes
